---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Fynite explains internet culture: the memes, slang, and viral moments everyone's talking about, and why they matter."
  canonical="/about"
>
  <section class="page-header page-container">
    <p class="eyebrow">About Fynite</p>
    <h1>We explain the internet, so you don't have to guess.</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">
      Something new blows up online every day &mdash; a meme, a phrase, a
      clip nobody can stop watching. Fynite exists to catch you up fast,
      without the jargon.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-body article-container">
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>
      Every story on Fynite answers the same three questions: what is this,
      where did it come from, and why is everyone talking about it. We cover
      memes, viral moments, internet slang, and the bigger online phenomena
      that shape how people communicate.
    </p>

    <h2>How we work</h2>
    <p>
      We research every story before we publish it. We check original
      sources, credit where a trend actually started when that's known, and
      say clearly when the origin of something is disputed or unclear &mdash;
      because on the internet, it often is.
    </p>
    <p>
      We write for people who live online, not for people studying it from
      the outside. That means plain language, no unnecessary jargon, and no
      pretending something is more complicated than it is.
    </p>

    <h2>Who's behind it</h2>
    <p>
      Fynite is an independent internet culture publication. We're not
      affiliated with any of the platforms, creators, or trends we cover.
    </p>

    <div class="page-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Read the latest stories</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding-top: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .page-header .eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.7rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .page-lede {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .page-body {
    padding-top: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .page-body h2 {
    margin-top: 2em;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .page-body h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .page-body p {
    margin-top: 1em;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .page-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 2.6em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .page-header {
      padding-top: 36px;
      padding-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .page-body {
      padding-top: 36px;
      padding-bottom: 56px;
    }
  }
</style>
